Asanza Lahabali

Jilimalana John Dramani Mahama nyɛla Ghana Tiŋgbaŋ Zuɣulana. O yila Bole din be Savannah yaɣili tiŋgbaŋ ni na ka lahi be Lem paati ni. O nyɛla bɛ ni daa dɔɣi so Damongo din be Damongo piibu-piibu yaɣili la din mi gba be Savanna Region Ghana pulini. O chɛŋ la Ghana Senior High School din be Tamale, tudu yaɣili.

Jilimalana Evans Atta Mills ni daa saŋ zaŋ o nuu n dihi buɣa tiŋa ka be daa piigi o tuuli tiŋgbaŋ zuɣulana. Jilimalana Mahama n daa nyɛ minisita zuɣulana paa n-zaŋ ti lahabaya tibu ni di wuligibu minisita tali silimiin' gɔli April yuuni 1997 hali ni November yuuni 1998.

Ŋuni n-daa lahi nyɛ chaamani zuɣulana paa zaŋ ti Publicity Committee din daa sɔŋdi lampoo Value Added Tax (VAT) labibu na.

Lahabali Din Gahim

Bagabaga College of Education(bɛ ni daa mi shɛli Bagabaga Training College, bee BATCO la) nyɛla karimzɔŋ karili din be Tamale (Sagnarigu Municipality, Northern region, Ghana) n-wumisiri karimbanimaKarimzɔŋ maa nyɛla din be Northern zone la ni. Di nyɛla Ghana tingbani ŋɔ ni karimbanima karim zɔndi din kalinli yiɣisi kaman pihinahi ni ayɔbu (46) la puuni yini. Silimiingoli January biɛɣu pihita ni yini dali (31 st),1944 yuuni ka bɛ daa kpa lala karimzɔŋ ŋɔ. Bɛ daa zaŋ la shikurubihi pia ni ayopɔin (17) m-pili [[shikuru ŋɔ, ka zaŋ tɛhisuma din nyɛ baŋsim lɛbu dini ni di che ka bɛ lee karimba maŋa n-wuhiri m mayaankalɛhi shikuriti. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla shikuru shɛli din ba daansi ni Sagnarigu Municipal Education duu la yaɣili ni Tamale Senior High School nti pahi Tamale Technical University karimzɔŋ kara la. Bagabaga College of Education (BACE), Tamale Technical University (TaTU), Tamale College of Education (TACE), Bagabaga Demonstration KG/PRIMARY/JHS zaa ka bɛ laɣim boli Education Ridge la Sagnarigu yaɣili la. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli din bɛ University of Education, Winnebanima fukumsi ni. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli ban wumsi karimbanima pam ka bɛ be bolli ni yiɣ'jam yaɣili Northern tudu yaɣili. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla ban kpaŋdi bɛ maŋ pam zaŋ chaŋ karimba mini karimmanima bɔhimbu polo

Asanza Lahabali

Jilimalana John Dramani Mahama nyɛla Ghana Tiŋgbaŋ Zuɣulana. O yila Bole din be Savannah yaɣili tiŋgbaŋ ni na ka lahi be Lem paati ni. O nyɛla bɛ ni daa dɔɣi so Damongo din be Damongo piibu-piibu yaɣili la din mi gba be Savanna Region Ghana pulini. O chɛŋ la Ghana Senior High School din be Tamale, tudu yaɣili.

Jilimalana Evans Atta Mills ni daa saŋ zaŋ o nuu n dihi buɣa tiŋa ka be daa piigi o tuuli tiŋgbaŋ zuɣulana. Jilimalana Mahama n daa nyɛ minisita zuɣulana paa n-zaŋ ti lahabaya tibu ni di wuligibu minisita tali silimiin' gɔli April yuuni 1997 hali ni November yuuni 1998.

Ŋuni n-daa lahi nyɛ chaamani zuɣulana paa zaŋ ti Publicity Committee din daa sɔŋdi lampoo Value Added Tax (VAT) labibu na.

Lahabali Din Gahim

Bagabaga College of Education(bɛ ni daa mi shɛli Bagabaga Training College, bee BATCO la) nyɛla karimzɔŋ karili din be Tamale (Sagnarigu Municipality, Northern region, Ghana) n-wumisiri karimbanimaKarimzɔŋ maa nyɛla din be Northern zone la ni. Di nyɛla Ghana tingbani ŋɔ ni karimbanima karim zɔndi din kalinli yiɣisi kaman pihinahi ni ayɔbu (46) la puuni yini. Silimiingoli January biɛɣu pihita ni yini dali (31 st),1944 yuuni ka bɛ daa kpa lala karimzɔŋ ŋɔ. Bɛ daa zaŋ la shikurubihi pia ni ayopɔin (17) m-pili [[shikuru ŋɔ, ka zaŋ tɛhisuma din nyɛ baŋsim lɛbu dini ni di che ka bɛ lee karimba maŋa n-wuhiri m mayaankalɛhi shikuriti. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla shikuru shɛli din ba daansi ni Sagnarigu Municipal Education duu la yaɣili ni Tamale Senior High School nti pahi Tamale Technical University karimzɔŋ kara la. Bagabaga College of Education (BACE), Tamale Technical University (TaTU), Tamale College of Education (TACE), Bagabaga Demonstration KG/PRIMARY/JHS zaa ka bɛ laɣim boli Education Ridge la Sagnarigu yaɣili la. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli din bɛ University of Education, Winnebanima fukumsi ni. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli ban wumsi karimbanima pam ka bɛ be bolli ni yiɣ'jam yaɣili Northern tudu yaɣili. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla ban kpaŋdi bɛ maŋ pam zaŋ chaŋ karimba mini karimmanima bɔhimbu polo

Jilimalana John Dramani Mahama, Ghana Tiŋgbaŋ Zuɣulana
Jilimalana John Dramani Mahama nyɛla Ghana Tiŋgbaŋ Zuɣulana. O yila Bole din be Savannah yaɣili tiŋgbaŋ ni na ka lahi be Lem paati ni. O nyɛla bɛ ni daa dɔɣi so Damongo din be Damongo piibu-piibu yaɣili la din mi gba be Savanna Region Ghana pulini. O chɛŋ la Ghana Senior High School din be Tamale, tudu yaɣili. 

Jilimalana Evans Atta Mills ni daa saŋ zaŋ o nuu n dihi buɣa tiŋa ka be daa piigi o tuuli tiŋgbaŋ zuɣulana. Jilimalana Mahama n daa nyɛ minisita zuɣulana paa n-zaŋ ti lahabaya tibu ni di wuligibu minisita tali silimiin' gɔli April yuuni 1997 hali ni November yuuni 1998.

Ŋuni n-daa lahi nyɛ chaamani zuɣulana paa zaŋ ti Publicity Committee din daa sɔŋdi lampoo Value Added Tax (VAT) labibu na.

Bagabaga College of Education(bɛ ni daa mi shɛli Bagabaga Training College, bee BATCO la) nyɛla karimzɔŋ karili din be Tamale (Sagnarigu Municipality, Northern region, Ghana) n-wumisiri karimbanimaKarimzɔŋ maa nyɛla din be Northern zone la ni. Di nyɛla Ghana tingbani ŋɔ ni karimbanima karim zɔndi din kalinli yiɣisi kaman pihinahi ni ayɔbu (46) la puuni yini. Silimiingoli January biɛɣu pihita ni yini dali (31 st),1944 yuuni ka bɛ daa kpa lala karimzɔŋ ŋɔ. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla shikuru shɛli din ba daansi ni Sagnarigu Municipal Education duu la yaɣili ni Tamale Senior High School nti pahi Tamale Technical University karimzɔŋ kara la. Bagabaga College of Education (BACE), Tamale Technical University (TaTU), Tamale College of Education (TACE), Bagabaga Demonstration KG/PRIMARY/JHS zaa ka bɛ laɣim boli Education Ridge la Sagnarigu yaɣili la. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli din bɛ University of Education, Winnebanima fukumsi ni. Jilimalana **[John Dramani Mahama](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Dramani_Mahama "John Dramani Mahama")** nyɛla [Ghana](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana "Ghana") Tiŋgbaŋ Zuɣulana. O yila [Bole](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bole "Bole") din be [Savannah yaɣili](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Savannah_Region "Savannah Region") tiŋgbaŋ ni na ka lahi be [Lem paati](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Democratic_Congress "National Democratic Congress") ni. O chɛŋ la [Ghana Senior High School](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana_Senior_High_School "Ghana Senior High School") din be [Tamale](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamale "Tamale"), [tudu yaɣili](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Region "Northern Region"). 
Jilimalana [Evans Atta Mills](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evans_Atta_Mills?action=edit&redlink=1 "Evans Atta Mills \(yaɣili ŋɔ maa kani\)") ni daa saŋ zaŋ o nuu n dihi buɣa tiŋa ka be daa piigi o tuuli tiŋgbaŋ zuɣulana. Jilimalana Mahama n daa nyɛ minisita zuɣulana paa n-zaŋ ti lahabaya tibu ni di wuligibu minisita tali silimiin' gɔli April yuuni 1997 hali ni November yuuni 1998.
Ŋuni n-daa lahi nyɛ chaamani zuɣulana paa zaŋ ti Publicity Committee din daa sɔŋdi lampoo Value Added Tax (VAT) labibu na.

**Bagabaga College of Education**(bɛ ni daa mi shɛli [Bagabaga Training College](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bagabaga_Training_College "Bagabaga Training College"), bee BATCO la) nyɛla [karimzɔŋ](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karimz%C9%94%C5%8B "Karimzɔŋ") karili din be [Tamale](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamali "Tamali") ([Sagnarigu Municipality](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sagnarigu_Municipality "Sagnarigu Municipality"), [Northern region](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Region "Northern Region"), Ghana) n-wumisiri karimbanimaKarimzɔŋ maa nyɛla din be [Northern](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Region "Northern Region") zone la ni. Di nyɛla Ghana [tingbani](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ti%C5%8Bgbani "Tiŋgbani") ŋɔ ni karimbanima karim zɔndi din kalinli yiɣisi kaman pihinahi ni ayɔbu (46) la puuni yini. [Silimiingoli](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silimiingoli "Silimiingoli") January biɛɣu pihita ni yini dali (31 st),1944 yuuni ka bɛ daa kpa lala karimzɔŋ ŋɔ. Bɛ daa zaŋ la [shikurubihi](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shikuru "Shikuru") pia ni ayopɔin (17) m-pili [[shikuru ŋɔ, ka zaŋ tɛhisuma din nyɛ [baŋsim](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ba%C5%8Bsim_dunoli:Alaafei_mini_Tilahi "Baŋsim dunoli:Alaafei mini Tilahi") lɛbu dini ni di che ka bɛ lee [karimba](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karimba_nima_dabisili "Karimba nima dabisili") maŋa n-wuhiri m mayaankalɛhi shikuriti. Bagabaga College of Education nyɛla shikuru shɛli din ba daansi ni [Sagnarigu Municipal Education](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sagnarigu_Municipal_Education "Sagnarigu Municipal Education") duu la yaɣili ni [Tamale Senior High School](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamale_Senior_High_School "Tamale Senior High School") nti pahi Tamale Technical University karimzɔŋ kara la. [Bagabaga College of Education](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bagabaga_College_of_Education "Bagabaga College of Education") (BACE), [Tamale Technical University](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamale_Technical_University "Tamale Technical University") [(TaTU)](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/\(TaTU\)?action=edit&redlink=1 "\(TaTU\) \(yaɣili ŋɔ maa kani\)"), [Tamale College of Education (TACE)](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamale_College_of_Education\(TACE\) "Tamale College of Education\(TACE\)"), [Bagabaga Demonstration KG/PRIMARY/JHS](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bagabaga_Demonstration_KG/PRIMARY/JHS "Bagabaga Demonstration KG/PRIMARY/JHS") zaa ka bɛ laɣim boli [Education Ridge](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education_Ridge "Education Ridge") la [Sagnarigu](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sagnarigu_Municipality "Sagnarigu Municipality") yaɣili la. [Bagabaga College of Education](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bagabaga_College_of_Education "Bagabaga College of Education") nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli din bɛ [University of Education, Winnebanima](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Education,_Winneba "University of Education, Winneba") fukumsi ni. [Bagabaga College of Education](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bagabaga_College_of_Education "Bagabaga College of Education") nyɛla karimzɔŋ shɛli ban wumsi karimbanima pam ka bɛ be bolli ni yiɣ'jam yaɣili [Northern](https://dag.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Region "Northern Region") tudu yaɣili.
